            <title>[LU-16591] include fix version in OCD</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16591</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If the &lt;tt&gt;LUSTRE_VERSION&lt;/tt&gt; definition in &lt;tt&gt;LUSTRE-VERSION-GEN&lt;/tt&gt; includes a vendor tag, such as &quot;&lt;tt&gt;2.14.0-abc123&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; include the vendor tag version (&quot;&lt;tt&gt;123&lt;/tt&gt;&quot;) as the &lt;tt&gt;LUSTRE_FIX&lt;/tt&gt; component in the &lt;tt&gt;ocd_version&lt;/tt&gt; field (i.e. &lt;tt&gt;2.14.0.123&lt;/tt&gt;).  This improves identification of remote client/server versions via the &lt;tt&gt;mdc.&amp;#42;.import&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;mdt.&amp;#42;.exports.&amp;#42;.export&lt;/tt&gt; parameters.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
